title: Word for Word: Sen. Rand Paul says vaccines give a false sense of security (C-SPAN)
description: At a hearing on vaccines and preventable outbreaks, Sen. Rand Paul says  it is wrong that to say there are no risks to vaccines. He and his kids are vaccinated because the benefits of vaccines outweighs the risks, but "I still do not favor giving up on liberty for a false sense of security." https://cs.pn/2ENk5Fn
